# CSS Grid Cheatsheet

## Container Properties

```css
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  grid-template-rows: auto;
  gap: 20px;
}
```

## Item Placement

```css
.item {
  grid-column: 1 / 3;  /* span 2 columns */
  grid-row: 1 / 2;
}
```

## Useful Functions

- `repeat(3, 1fr)` - Repeat pattern
- `minmax(100px, 1fr)` - Min and max sizes
- `auto-fill` - Fill available space
- `auto-fit` - Fit content
